OL,6,FUTV can exclusively reveal that
OL,7,FMacCormack was caught by Gardai in
OL,8,FDublin in April 2021 with almost
OL,9,FE22,000 worth of the Class A drug in a
OL,10,Fblack bin liner in his van.
OL,12,FThe 71-year-old pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fpossession of the drug and released on
OL,14,Fcontinuing bail pending sentence the
OL,15,Fday before he was arrested in Belfast.
OL,17,FSources have said the heroin was meant
OL,18,Ffor the young vulnerable women he used
OL,19,Fand abused.
